---
title: Spiced Lamb Moussaka with a Crispy Panko Topping
description: This moussaka is just a little bit different to your regular run-of-the-mill moussaka! Despite having the traditional spiced lamb and creamy flavours of a moussaka, it also involves charred courgettes (instead of aubergine) and pasta! This really is deliciously comforting 'treat food', perfect for a midweek meal
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spiced-lamb-moussaka-00d5d82a-ce6a395e.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/spiced-lamb-moussaka-5b36145030006c41c71bd072-442a9d53.pdf
